"      Lanicor (AE, AR, AT, BB, BF, BH, BJ, BM, BS, BZ, CI, CY, CZ, DE, EC, EG, ET, GH, GM, GN, GR, GY, HR, IQ, IR, JM, JO, KE, KW, LB, LR, LU, LY, MA, ML, MR, MU, MW, NE, NG, OM, QA, SA, SC, SD, SL, SN, SR, SY, TN, TT, TZ, UG, VE, YE, ZM, ZW);",
"     </li>",
"     <li>",
"      Lanikor (RU);",
"     </li>",
